# Runtime messages

When adding or changing a message:

1. Extend unions in `extension/core/types/messages.ts` (or domain type files re-exported from `index.ts`).
2. Route in `extension/core/background/handlers.ts` with type guards.
3. Update `extension/core/background/sender-auth.ts` for content-originated messages.
4. Add handler in matching domain `background/handlers.ts`.
5. Add/adjust tests in `tests/core/handlers-*.test.ts` or domain tests.

Background → content messages use `chrome.tabs.sendMessage` and bypass `handleMessage`.
